---
// src/components/ComplianceProblem.astro
const regulations = [
  { src: '/assets/CRA.svg', alt: 'CRA'},
  { src: '/assets/NIS2.svg', alt: 'NIS2'},
  { src: '/assets/DORA.svg', alt: 'DORA'},
  { src: '/assets/ISO27001.svg', alt: 'ISO 27001'},
  { src: '/assets/GDPR.svg', alt: 'GDPR'},
];
---

<section class="compliance-section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">The Challenge</span>
    <h2>A perfect storm is coming for compliance</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-container">
    <div class="stats-col">
      <div class="card regulations-card">
        <div class="icons-row">
          {regulations.map(reg => (
            <div class="icon-wrapper">
              <img src={reg.src} alt={reg.alt} />
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p>New regulations bring complex legal obligations and severe penalties.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="card stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">85%</div>
          <p>Of companies would not pass a compliance audit today.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">30%</div>
          <p>More vulnerable to cyber attacks when not compliant.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card dilemma-col">
      <span class="eyebrow">The Dilemma</span>
      <h3>To be or not to be (compliant)</h3>
      <div class="dilemma-content">
        <p>
          Achieving compliance <strong class="highlight">costs significant time and resources</strong> without directly generating income.
        </p>
        <p class="risk-text">
          Failing to comply means risking fines up to <strong class="highlight">â‚¬10 million</strong> and being <strong class="highlight">forced out of the market.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .compliance-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .eyebrow {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .grid-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: rgba(17, 17, 21, 0.4);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  /* Stats Column */
  .stats-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .regulations-card p {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .icons-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    padding: 10px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .icon-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .stat-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Dilemma Column */
  .dilemma-col h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }
  
  .dilemma-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .risk-text {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    .card {
        padding: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>